TDFam is an open-source TouchDesigner framework for creating, registering,
distributing, and updating custom operator families. It includes the TDFam
core, TD Registry, menu integration, manifest system, stubbing and update
tools, callbacks, configuration import/export, examples, documentation, and
related support files distributed with this project.

